OL,3,CBirmingham City Council leader claims
OL,4,Cauthority is no longer 'bankrupt'
OL,6,FThe proposal includes a 4.99% council
OL,7,Ftax rise - the highest possible
OL,8,Fwithout special permission from
OL,9,Fgovernment or a local referendum.
OL,11,FThe council also will not seek any
OL,12,Ffurther EFS (Exceptional Financial
OL,13,FSupport).
OL,15,FThere will still be cuts of #93m in
OL,16,Fthe 26/27 budget.JBut the leader
OL,17,Finsists this will be met through
OL,18,Fefficiency savings, NOT service cuts.
