OL,3,CBirmingham City Council leader claims
OL,4,Cauthority is no longer 'bankrupt'
OL,6,FThe council says it wants to invest in
OL,7,Fcleaner, safer streets and better
OL,8,Flocal services.
OL,10,FThe proposed budget will be discussed
OL,11,Fat Cabinet on 10th February, before
OL,12,Fcouncillors vote on the proposals at
OL,13,FFull Council on the 24th February.
