OL,3,CBirmingham City Council leader claims
OL,4,Cauthority is no longer 'bankrupt'
OL,6,FCllr John Cotton said:
OL,8,F"The council is no longer under a
OL,9,FSection 114 Notice. Thanks to the
OL,10,Fdecisive, tough action we took to get
OL,11,Fthe council back on track, the
OL,12,F'bankrupt Birmingham' tag is now a
OL,13,Fthing of the past.
OL,15,F"This is a significant moment in the
OL,16,Fcouncil's recovery and is down to the
OL,17,Fsheer hard work that has been
OL,18,Fundertaken here in Birmingham by
OL,19,Fmembers and officers, supported by
OL,20,Fcommissioners.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
